## ✅ COMPLETED BEFORE TODAY: Phase 13 (Compliance & Audit)

### Implementation Summary
Successfully implemented complete Compliance & Audit system for CASCI including:

#### Audit System
- ✅ Audit event models with full metadata tracking
- ✅ SQL repository with filtering, querying, and cleanup
- ✅ Audit service with 90-day retention default
- ✅ Automatic cleanup scheduler (runs daily)
- ✅ HTTP API handlers for audit management
- ✅ Database migrations for all 3 DB types (SQLite, PostgreSQL, MySQL)
- ✅ Performance indexes (user_id, timestamp, action, resource)

#### Compliance System
- ✅ 6 compliance mode presets (HIPAA, SOX, PCI-DSS, GDPR, FedRAMP, ISO27001)
- ✅ Compliance checks with severity levels
- ✅ Compliance reports with findings and recommendations
- ✅ HTTP API handlers for compliance management
- ✅ Password policy validation per mode
- ✅ Session timeout enforcement
- ✅ Data retention policy configuration

#### Integration
- ✅ Integrated into main server (src/pkg/server/server.go)
- ✅ Added 10 new API endpoints for audit and compliance
- ✅ Tested build successfully (24MB static binary)
- ✅ Updated all documentation (README.md, TODO.md, SUMMARY.md, TODO.AI.md)

