### API Endpoints Added (10 total)
1. `GET /api/v1/audit/events` - List audit events
2. `GET /api/v1/audit/status` - Get audit status
3. `PUT /api/v1/audit/config` - Update audit configuration
4. `POST /api/v1/audit/cleanup` - Trigger manual cleanup
5. `GET /api/v1/compliance/config` - Get compliance configuration
6. `PUT /api/v1/compliance/config` - Update compliance configuration
7. `GET /api/v1/compliance/modes` - List available compliance modes
8. `POST /api/v1/compliance/mode` - Set compliance mode
9. `GET /api/v1/compliance/preset` - Get preset for a mode
10. `POST /api/v1/compliance/check` - Run compliance check

